OL,5, DUP leader Sir Jeffrey Donaldson has   
OL,6, branded P&O Ferries "a disgrace" for   
OL,7, the way it sacked 800 workers.         
OL,9,FMany workers were told without warning 
OL,10,Fby video message on Thursday that it   
OL,11,Fwould be "their final day of           
OL,12,Femployment".                           
OL,14,FP&O sailings between Larne and         
OL,15,FCairnryan have been disrupted since    
OL,16,Fthen.                                  
OL,18,FIt could be another week before the    
OL,19,Fcompany's ferries can operate from the 
OL,20,FCounty Antrim port.                    
